614
00:26:35,970 --> 00:26:36,570
News of this

615
00:26:36,570 --> 00:26:38,160
has spread through the company.

616
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,760
Mr. Feng is quite concerned.

617
00:26:40,090 --> 00:26:40,850
After all,

618
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:42,630
Wu Jiang is Xinhai's Vice President.

619
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:44,230
If something happens to him,

620
00:26:44,250 --> 00:26:46,270
it won't look good for the company.

621
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:48,440
Can you reveal

622
00:26:48,550 --> 00:26:49,130
what exactly he...

623
00:26:49,130 --> 00:26:49,890
Mr. Meng.

624
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:51,660
For a company as big as Xinhai,

625
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:53,050
before you hire someone,

626
00:26:53,050 --> 00:26:54,850
don't you do background checks?

627
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:58,040
Of course we do background checks.

628
00:26:58,510 --> 00:26:59,240
However,

629
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:00,460
people

630
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:01,570
always have a past.

631
00:27:02,190 --> 00:27:03,490
What we can find

632
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:04,260
isn't much.

633
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:05,980
Then how did he

634
00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:07,970
get into Xinhai in the first place?

635
00:27:09,380 --> 00:27:10,440
Mr. Feng hired him.

636
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:12,090
I don't know the details.

637
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:13,310
But over the years,

638
00:27:13,310 --> 00:27:14,640
he's done well at Xinhai

639
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:16,710
and hasn't caused any trouble.

640
00:27:18,420 --> 00:27:19,530
Then regarding Wu Jiang's background,

641
00:27:19,530 --> 00:27:20,660
how much do you know?

642
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:22,430
For example,

643
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:23,540
the time

644
00:27:23,570 --> 00:27:24,380
when he worked

645
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:26,030
at Mazhi Hongyuan Freight Company.

646
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:27,750
Hongyuan Freight?

647
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:29,250
I don't know.

648
00:27:30,670 --> 00:27:31,460
I know

649
00:27:31,490 --> 00:27:33,150
he worked in freight early on.

650
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:34,940
What kind of goods did he transport?

651
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:36,340
Who did he interact with most?

652
00:27:36,340 --> 00:27:38,440
Did you hear him mention these things?

653
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,150
I really don't know about that.

654
00:27:40,150 --> 00:27:40,640
After all, that was

655
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:42,300
before he joined the company.

656
00:27:43,350 --> 00:27:44,510
If you want to know,

657
00:27:44,970 --> 00:27:45,550
I can actually

658
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:47,280
ask around indirectly for you.

659
00:27:51,570 --> 00:27:52,330
Does this company

660
00:27:52,330 --> 00:27:54,260
have anything to do with your work?

661
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:57,290
Do you realize just now

662
00:27:57,290 --> 00:27:59,490
how many times you said you didn't know?

663
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:07,820
We're at a restaurant,

664
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,920
not a police station.

665
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:11,880
Why is it every time we chat,

666
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:14,010
it feels like I'm being interrogated?

667
00:28:14,730 --> 00:28:15,770
You feel that way?

668
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:18,900
Then maybe,

669
00:28:18,970 --> 00:28:20,630
