670
00:28:25,660 --> 00:28:27,660
It's just your professional habit.

671
00:28:33,870 --> 00:28:35,330
Sorry, I have to take this.

672
00:28:37,450 --> 00:28:37,950
Hello?

673
00:28:38,610 --> 00:28:39,050
Mom.

674
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:40,750
When are you coming back?

675
00:28:40,750 --> 00:28:42,110
I have something to tell you.

676
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:42,960
It's huge.

677
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:43,900
I know.

678
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:44,920
You got into a fight at school today,

679
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:45,840
