680
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,610
I'll deal with you when I get back.

681
00:28:47,610 --> 00:28:49,240
Don't listen to the teacher.

682
00:28:49,500 --> 00:28:51,640
He pulled my braid first.

683
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:52,330
Shao Zhuling,

684
00:28:52,330 --> 00:28:53,990
