688
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,750
You're half a head taller than that boy.

689
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:00,710
One push from you, and he goes flying.

690
00:29:00,710 --> 00:29:01,830
Do you know your own strength?

691
00:29:01,830 --> 00:29:03,550
I know.

692
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:04,380
If he hadn't fallen,

693
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:05,800
you would have kicked him, right?

694
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:07,200
The moves I taught you

695
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:08,380
are for defending against bad guys.

696
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:08,940
How could you use them

697
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:10,000
on your classmate?

698
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:12,440
What if you seriously

699
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:13,170
injured him?

700
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,480
I wouldn't.

701
00:29:15,350 --> 00:29:16,410
If you fight again,

702
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,160
I'll drive the police car over

703
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,020
and arrest you.

704
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:18,480
You...

705
00:29:18,730 --> 00:29:20,190
We'll talk when I get back.

706
00:29:21,590 --> 00:29:22,380
Sorry about that.

707
00:29:22,380 --> 00:29:23,810
My kid is a handful.

708
00:29:24,900 --> 00:29:25,500
It's fine.

709
00:29:26,380 --> 00:29:28,070
I feel a bit more balanced now.

710
00:29:30,840 --> 00:29:32,140
It's like you're interrogating

711
00:29:32,140 --> 00:29:33,250
everyone.

712
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,550
I've been forced into this.

713
00:29:36,550 --> 00:29:37,810
You heard that just now.

714
00:29:37,810 --> 00:29:38,850
It's so worrying.

715
00:29:40,390 --> 00:29:41,850
Having a child at home

716
00:29:42,010 --> 00:29:42,640
is lively.

717
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:44,910
Stop with the snide remarks.

718
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:46,140
If it's good to have kids,

719
00:29:46,140 --> 00:29:47,870
then why don't you get married?

720
00:29:48,610 --> 00:29:50,270
Then why did you get divorced?

721
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:51,790
Don't change the subject.

722
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:53,570
Fine.

723
00:29:56,590 --> 00:29:57,320
Officer Bai.

724
00:29:58,330 --> 00:29:59,400
I'm not married

725
00:29:59,910 --> 00:30:00,370
because

726
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:02,110
I haven't met the right person.

727
00:30:02,980 --> 00:30:03,870
After all, this kind of thing

728
00:30:03,870 --> 00:30:05,000
depends on fate,

729
00:30:05,220 --> 00:30:05,770
right?

730
00:30:21,030 --> 00:30:22,360
What are you doing here?

731
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:23,360
You went to eat?

732
00:30:24,770 --> 00:30:25,830
Or should I starve?

733
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,180
With whom?

734
00:30:28,090 --> 00:30:28,670
No one.

735
00:30:30,050 --> 00:30:30,660
No one?

736
00:30:31,660 --> 00:30:32,150
I heard

737
00:30:32,170 --> 00:30:33,500
it wasn't just "no one."

738
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:36,900
Bai Ji, that turncoat.

739
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,400
Don't blame Bai Ji.

740
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:41,610
We're worried about you.

741
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:42,590
You should

742
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:43,850
worry about yourself.

743
00:30:45,100 --> 00:30:46,430
That man is Meng Yaohui,

744
00:30:46,850 --> 00:30:48,330
General Manager of Xinhai.

745
00:30:48,330 --> 00:30:49,610
He's my blind date.

746
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:54,850
What are you laughing at?

747
00:30:56,230 --> 00:30:57,640
Then... I'm relieved.

748
00:30:59,390 --> 00:31:00,220
Shao Yunfei.

749
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,710
Did you not hear me?

750
00:31:03,570 --> 00:31:04,570
I just said

751
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:06,860
that was my blind date.

752
00:31:07,370 --> 00:31:08,610
My mom set us up.

753
00:31:09,610 --> 00:31:10,700
I... I heard you.

754
00:31:11,050 --> 00:31:12,460
You have a blind date.

755
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:15,060
But over the years,

756
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:16,360
