757
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:18,700
You scared them off immediately.

758
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,480
In Tianduo, there are so many

759
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:22,120
older single men,

760
00:31:22,150 --> 00:31:24,280
and you've roasted almost all of them.

761
00:31:24,550 --> 00:31:26,150
And which one has worked out?

762
00:31:27,930 --> 00:31:28,570
This isn't our

763
00:31:28,570 --> 00:31:29,770
first meal together.

764
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:39,530
Are you serious?

765
00:31:42,710 --> 00:31:43,650
No.

766
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:46,050
We have a work connection.

767
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:50,750
How many times have you met?

768
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:51,930
You are so annoying.

769
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:52,980
It's none of your business.

770
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:54,270
It has nothing to do with you.

771
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:55,400
Bai Ju, listen to me.

772
00:31:56,210 --> 00:31:57,260
For some interactions,

773
00:31:57,260 --> 00:31:59,190
you might think they mean nothing.

774
00:31:59,330 --> 00:31:59,580
But

775
00:31:59,610 --> 00:32:01,110
he might not think so.

776
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:04,750
Shao Yunfei.

777
00:32:05,310 --> 00:32:05,850
After all these years,

778
00:32:05,850 --> 00:32:07,050
you haven't changed.

779
00:32:08,010 --> 00:32:08,720
Not everyone

780
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:09,480
is like you,

781
00:32:09,850 --> 00:32:11,630
