782
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,350
Hunting for romance?

783
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:15,430
That sounds terrible.

784
00:32:15,430 --> 00:32:16,370
How can you compare him

785
00:32:16,370 --> 00:32:17,310
to us?

786
00:32:18,010 --> 00:32:19,310
We went through so much back then.

787
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:20,410
We came together

788
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:20,960
