792
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:31,110
What's her name?

793
00:32:31,150 --> 00:32:32,370
Xiaodong,

794
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,900
Xiaoxi, or whatever.

795
00:32:34,610 --> 00:32:35,250
Xi?

796
00:32:36,760 --> 00:32:38,220
You mean Xiaodong?

797
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:38,890
Whatever.

798
00:32:38,970 --> 00:32:39,400
Well.

799
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:40,360
You...

800
00:32:40,570 --> 00:32:41,380
Y-You...

801
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,660
Explain what you mean.

802
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:43,550
Don't you dare

803
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:44,480
