804
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:45,770
Shao Yunfei,

805
00:32:45,770 --> 00:32:46,770
stop pretending.

806
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,140
I saw it all.

807
00:32:48,660 --> 00:32:49,700
She texted you in the middle of the night,

808
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:50,360
calling you

809
00:32:51,060 --> 00:32:52,660
Handsome Shao or something.

810
00:32:53,660 --> 00:32:55,390
You really think you're a hunk?

811
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:56,920
That is a nickname

812
00:32:56,930 --> 00:32:57,750
