813
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:59,220
Everyone calls me that.

814
00:32:59,250 --> 00:32:59,740
Whatever.

815
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:00,570
It's been years.

816
00:33:00,570 --> 00:33:01,160
Explain it

817
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,160
however you want.

818
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:03,530
Besides, Xiaodong

819
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:04,880
was my junior at school.

820
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:05,870
She was assigned to our newspaper office,

821
00:33:05,870 --> 00:33:07,240
so I had to mentor her.

822
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:09,220
And she's already married.

823
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:11,040
They were college sweethearts.

824
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,590
Her husband was my junior too.

825
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:14,030
We were all close friends.

826
00:33:14,030 --> 00:33:15,290
Why are you twisting it like this?

827
00:33:15,290 --> 00:33:17,480
Fine, you were close.

828
00:33:18,090 --> 00:33:19,890
Go live with the two of them then.

829
00:33:20,280 --> 00:33:21,910
What do you mean by living with them?

830
00:33:21,910 --> 00:33:22,370
You...

831
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,980
It's been 4 years.

832
00:33:24,010 --> 00:33:25,590
Why bring this up now?

833
00:33:25,610 --> 00:33:26,410
Wait a minute.

834
00:33:28,570 --> 00:33:30,040
D-Did you divorce me

835
00:33:30,070 --> 00:33:31,180
because of this?

836
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:33,270
Our divorce

837
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:34,720
wasn't about one thing.

838
00:33:35,500 --> 00:33:35,980
Nor did it happen

839
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:37,220
overnight.

840
00:33:37,340 --> 00:33:37,830
If I had known

841
00:33:37,830 --> 00:33:38,480
it was because of this,

842
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,850
I would never have agreed

843
00:33:39,850 --> 00:33:40,680
to the divorce.

844
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,660
You know perfectly well

845
00:33:41,660 --> 00:33:43,010
why I divorced you.

846
00:33:43,140 --> 00:33:43,880
Here we go again.

847
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:44,610
What did I do?

848
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,660
All these years,

849
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:50,330
you've never told me

850
00:33:50,900 --> 00:33:52,200
what's on your mind.

851
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:54,130
You always make decisions,

852
00:33:54,130 --> 00:33:55,130
and I just follow.

853
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:55,830
Bai Ju.

854
00:33:57,120 --> 00:33:58,410
I care about you.

855
00:33:59,340 --> 00:34:00,600
I'm worried about you.

856
00:34:01,630 --> 00:34:02,810
Don't you understand?

857
00:34:02,810 --> 00:34:03,810
I still want to...

858
00:34:03,830 --> 00:34:04,500
I'm sorry.

859
00:34:08,150 --> 00:34:09,650
Since the Mountain Patrol was disbanded,

860
00:34:09,650 --> 00:34:10,580
all these years,

861
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:14,830
I haven't had a good night's sleep.

862
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,010
Work.

863
00:34:17,650 --> 00:34:18,570
Life.

864
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,190
Our child.

865
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:24,290
I can't handle any of them well.

866
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:26,510
But I'm trying hard

867
00:34:26,540 --> 00:34:27,810
to be a good mother.

868
00:34:28,650 --> 00:34:30,000
I'm doing my best

869
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:31,230
to be good to Zhuling.

870
00:34:33,659 --> 00:34:35,389
I know you care about the child.

871
00:34:36,239 --> 00:34:36,880
Thank you.

872
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,400
But it's been 4 years.

873
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,920
We're used to it by now.

874
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,400
I decided to separate.

875
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:47,389
And I don't regret it.

876
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:51,940
I held you back,

877
00:34:51,969 --> 00:34:52,699
Shao Yunfei.

878
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:57,940
Have I

879
00:34:59,780 --> 00:35:00,940
made myself clear?

880
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:20,470
Where are you going?

881
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:22,770
I rented a place up there.

882
00:35:26,050 --> 00:35:27,510
Who are you kidding?

883
00:35:28,420 --> 00:35:29,080
Seriously.

884
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,740
I've been transferred back.

885
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:38,540
You think you can go

