960
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:15,920
Hello?

961
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,370
Director Huang.

962
00:38:25,110 --> 00:38:25,550
Okay.

963
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:27,110
Okay.

964
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:28,430
